Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.67,0:00:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.49,0:00:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.14,0:01:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise the anchor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.09,0:02:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set the sails!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bring the ship forward!\N--You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't shake things, Sanji!\N--Full speed ahead to the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.76,0:02:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. If you're scared, then go\Ndown and sleep like a good li'l boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-D-Don't be stupid!\NOf course I'm not scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.77,0:02:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sanji! Breakfast!\N--Yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.44,0:02:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get started on it. Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Sanji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Hey, Zoro. Let's play tag.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, what?! Tag?!\NLet's play, let's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys stupid?!\NYou're pathetic, playing at your age!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna get some more\Nsleep before breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.03,0:02:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?! 'Cause you\Ndon't like losing, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!\NI don't give a damn about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--See! You're suddenly mad!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.74,0:03:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the truth, isn't it?! Bleehhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean you'll\Njoin our crew now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm only teaming up\Nwith you, just so you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always remember that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm over here! Come get me!\N--C'mon, Zoro! Chase me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not playing here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! Your meal's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys! Food's on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.84,0:03:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! I'm not done with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even after he said all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What, Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Food! Food! Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This looks yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what do you suppose\Nhappened to Buggy after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.89,0:03:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy? Oh, that Buggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:04:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? Maybe he's\Nat the bottom of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be so sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are a stubborn lot,\Nevery last one of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who kept\Nchasing me stubbornly! Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hunted pirates for years. I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that it matters,\Nbut your food's gone, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.99,0:04:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here you are, Nami-san!\N--Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A Special Yogurt Dessert!\N--You stole my food again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh! Thank you, Sanji-kun!\N--Give it back, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally finished my flashy raft!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, the great and world-renowned\Npirate, Buggy the Clown-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will get my crew back together\Nand get my super flashy revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what obstacles lie in my path!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The score must be settled!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn flashy\Nrubber man! Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely will beat you senseless\Nand make you cry uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff like this already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to lose! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Chase Straw Hat!\NLittle Buggy's Big Adventure"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to make it...\Nto the next island...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not some kind of exhibit, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...! Are you mocking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got some real guts, ridiculing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna eatcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just feeling hungry, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.37,0:06:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've made me mad!\NYou're done for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna eat you flashily,\Nso just give yourself up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.79,0:06:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop-Chop Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit your flailing!\NJust accept your fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.71,0:07:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.58,0:07:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My plan is flawless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum! Yum! Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got caught?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did things turn out this way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.16,0:07:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the end already?! This sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...! Am I that bad-tasting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a little bit of a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! A hermit crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.22,0:08:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when he got on\Nboard. At Nami's village?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably. That, or maybe\Nat Usopp's village?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, that's incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd mean he's been\Ntraveling with us this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Why does this happen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Did you just say something?\N--Huh? Me? I didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nuh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird. Must've\Nbeen my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, Luffy! Quit slackin' off!\N--Oh! Sorry! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am this island's protective god!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this island at once\Nif you value your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protective god?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! You're one of those, uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...weird creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kick your ass, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! Just try taking\Nanother step into the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The instant you do, will you\Nreceive my divine punishment
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.57,0:09:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and meet your doom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know, you flashy idiot?!\NWhy're you asking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The animals of this forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with them,\Nunless you want to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:10:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? These are some\Nflashily interesting animals...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to go any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast it! He suddenly shot at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Come out!\N--Oww! Oww! Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! You have a Devil Fruit power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if I do?! You're nothing--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a boxed and sheltered son?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I've been overly pampered\Nsince I was just a little boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.30,0:10:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do stupid gags!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! Don't get cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.17,0:10:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't show mercy to anyone\Nwho messes with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You wanna fight me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:11:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I commend your bravery,\Nbut don't blame me after you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.13,0:11:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flying weapons are unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's this thing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.91,0:12:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk so selfishly!\NSay your prayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop-Chop Quick Escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How dare you?! Blast it! Oww!\N--How dare I what?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad! Anyone who messes\Nwith the animals has to pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're this island's treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those weird animals are treasures?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:13:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure refers to gold, silver,\Nand jewels, you flashy idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play stupid! You came to\Nthis island to get these animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I do that?! I didn't\Ncome here 'cause I wanted to!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you're not a poacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! I might not\Nlook it, but I'm a great pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Buggy the Clown-sama!\NI'd never do anything as mean as that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate? You're a pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too! I used to be a\Npirate a long time ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my bad! My bad!\NSo you're a pirate, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whadya think? Good, huh?!\NIt's my own unrefined sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:14:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is the best! How many\Ndays it's been since I last drank...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have as many refills\Nas you want! Drink up and up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm really sorry about earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just assumed you were a poacher\Nwho came to get these animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.98,0:14:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was some horrible stuff you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't matter now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus you let me have\Nthis delicious booze, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only things in this world that\Ninterest me are treasure and alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.20,0:14:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm likin' you even more!\NYou're a pirate, all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a real stout-hearted guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, why are you on this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I originally came here\Nin search of treasure, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! There's treasure on this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. If there was, I wouldn't\Nbe hanging around here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh. You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.42,0:14:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, some stuff happened\Nand my crew left me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I've been calling this island\Nhome for the past 20 years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20 years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've really had it rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so bad, really.\NThese guys are here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way of life is actually pretty\Nnice once you get used to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno. I'd much rather be living\Nthe pirate life with my crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.09,0:15:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True, pirate life is nice! It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.19,0:15:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I would gladly risk my life to\Ngo on treasure-hunting adventures!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?! It's like, "Hurray for pirates!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say? When I get my\Npirate crew back, won't you join us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.84,0:15:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I greatly welcome guys like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you have the pirate spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Whadya say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:16:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... inviting me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate the thought,\Nbut these guys are my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you live with them for\N20 years, they rub off on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if they are weird creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.65,0:16:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I was just\Nremembering a young pirate
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who asked me to be a pirate\Nagain just like you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.19,0:16:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so upset, old guy!\NIt's a good thing we came after 20 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30 years later and you\Nmight've been dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.00,0:16:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was such an incredibly nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.44,0:17:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you and him'd be good friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So there are\Nyoungsters out there like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not me, though.\NI ran into this one horrible kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assemble! Chop-Chop Parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tadah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.03,0:17:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking for these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go flying, Buggy! Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how I wound up\Non a wandering journey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.88,0:17:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just thinking about it now\Nmakes me boil with rage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Sorry to hear what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it just goes to show there are\Nall kinds of youngsters out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, let's have fun tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want this\Nnight to go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:18:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--To pirates!\N--And to us meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for asking you\Nto help make a raft, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.52,0:18:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. It was my pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're really going to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. With all my friends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, friend! Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.39,0:18:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Buggy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many strange\Ncreatures in these waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be ever careful on your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I forgot to tell him that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Run, Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.27,0:19:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Look out! Run! Get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's super pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at least it looks like he's saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.69,0:20:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had me sweating bullets there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, take care of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the help! I flashily\Nthought I was a goner there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Buggy the Clown, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:21:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?! Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for a certain man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.02,0:21:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn rubber man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you! Someday, I will settle\Nthe score with you! Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.27,0:21:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the guy you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come. I have a meal ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's why you helped me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.45,0:21:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you say?\NWill you team up with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, why not?\NWe both have the same goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.66,0:21:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.83,0:21:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great. Then cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.14,0:21:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.78,0:22:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji... Food...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just ate... Gimme a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.16,0:22:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you guys... I can't sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sleep too much... Help out\Nwith work sometimes... Sheesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.67,0:22:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed they can hold\Nconversations in their sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.34,0:22:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about skillful...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.01,0:22:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I'll hit the hay, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.28,0:22:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.07,0:23:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.76,0:23:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.76,0:23:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.33,0:23:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.81,0:23:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.56,0:23:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.56,0:24:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.47,0:24:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Buggy's\Nhenchmen were neat, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.18,0:24:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you mean like the\Nunicycle guy and the lion guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.88,0:24:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Cabaji and Mohji, was it?\N--He had animals, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.45,0:24:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they really pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.29,0:24:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think is their captain now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.92,0:24:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cabaji or Mohji, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.09,0:24:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? Maybe it's that lion!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.16,0:24:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.42,0:24:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Wait is Over!\NThe Return of Captain Buggy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.36,0:24:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.40,0:24:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
